{
  "stem": "13395.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They might have been their friends at one time, but now they were told that they cannot associate with them anymore, and so the Jews were isolated.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the propaganda of Goebbels and Streicher with his which, by the way, I have a copy of here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the propaganda and the lies and the way the Jews were portrayed as the enemies of the people, of the German people, and how they were blamed for all the awful things and for the loss of the war and what the Allies did to Germany.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They incited them to become anti-Semites.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Children-- now, remember, children joined the Nazi youth organization in 1933.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If a child was 15, in 1938, he was 18.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And if he was brainwashed to hate the Jews, and so many reasons were given to him, it wasn't difficult to become an anti-Semite and hate the Jews.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You blame them for every-- all the ills of the country and of the people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, definitely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was even before, because there was unemployment in the-- the-- the mines did not work for a time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was all a ploy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, most of the mines in Upper Silesia were owned by Germans, because this was Germany.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was in Hitler's interest to create unemployment across the border.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the German owners slowly closed the mines for no reason at all other than having those people unemployed and create unrest.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And now your counterparts on the other side of the border work day and night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There is no unemployment under the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So you can see the political implications here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Consequently-- the people that were real friends would come at night through the back door when no one saw them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The rest of them would not come.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
